  <brief_title>Clinical Study on Diagnostics and Outcome of Ruptures of the Subscapularis After Arthroscopic Refixation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Multicenter Trial on Diagnostics and Outcome of Ruptures of the Subscapularis After Arthroscopic Refixation</official_title>
